# CONTEXT SEED — Esskultur Cloudflare Platform (Development State)

## 1. Project goal

Build a **Restaurant Operating Platform** for Esskultur.

The system architecture:

```
Cloudflare Workers = platform logic
Cloudflare D1 = source of truth
Odoo Online = ERP mirror
Staff mobile web app = operation interface
```

The goal is to support:

```
multi-restaurant
franchise model
fully automated booking management
```

---

# 2. Core architecture

```
Customer
   ↓
Website form
   ↓
Cloudflare Worker
   ↓
D1 database (source of truth)
   ↓
Staff mobile web app
   ↓
Odoo CRM / ERP mirror
```

Important rule:

```
Cloudflare D1 = master
Odoo = mirror
```

