# 6. Stage system

Booking stage runtime values:

```
pending
confirmed
arrived
done
cancelled
noshow
```

Stage mapping to Odoo:

```
pending    → 1
confirmed  → 2
arrived    → 3
done       → 4
cancelled  → 5
noshow     → 6
```

Cloudflare stage engine controls:

```
stage_runtime
stage_id
```

Odoo only mirrors `stage_id`.

