# 7. Current APIs implemented

### list bookings

```
GET /api/admin/bookings
```

Returns:

```
items[]
```

Fields include:

```
booking_time
contact_name
phone
x_studio_guests
x_studio_required_blocks
x_studio_stage_runtime
x_studio_source
updated_at
```

---

### change stage

```
POST /api/admin/stage
```

Payload:

```
{
  booking_id,
  stage
}
```

Worker updates:

```
stage_runtime
stage_id
updated_at
```

and logs event into:

```
booking_stage_log
```

